\sum_{k=0}^{\lfloor \frac n2\rfloor} {13\choose k}{4\choose2}^k{13-k\choose n-2k}{4\choose1}^{n-2k}=4^n\sum_{k=0}^{\lfloor \frac n2\rfloor} {13\choose k}{13-k\choose n-2k}\Bigl(\frac38\Bigr)^k.
